header.gameNote: FRONTIER COMMUNICATIONS AMERICAN ATHLETIC CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Tigers guard K.J. Lawson finds a streaking Jimario Rivers for the one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Lawson finds Rivers to put Memphis up by six points early

videos.description: A.J. Davis steps up and drains the three for UCF, part of a 18-0 run for the Knights.
videos.headline: Davis nails the 3-pointer for UCF

videos.description: UCF forward Nick Banyard increases the Knights' big lead as he drains the long two, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Banyard nails the jumper for UCF, plus the foul

videos.description: UCF big man Tacko Fall slams it with ease to put the Knights up 56-29
videos.headline: Fall gets the pass inside and finishes with the dunk

videos.description: Matt Williams sinks his fifth 3-pointer of the game as he gives the Knights a 22-point lead.
videos.headline: Williams drains the long three for UCF

videos.description: B.J. Taylor lobs one up for Tacko Fall, who finishes easily with the slam.
videos.headline: Taylor finds Fall for the alley-oop slam to increase UCF's lead
